title: Feature: Ten People Who Don't Know Who Kurt Cobain Is
body:
Apparently it would have been Kurt Cobain’s 46th birthday today, not much use if you don’t even know who Kurt Cobain was…

> Guys, who is Kurt Cobain? I have no idea who the hell that is…
> 
> — Alisonn Fizzy ♥ (@alisonnnnnx3) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/alisonnnnnx3/status/304268280275816448)

> Who is kurt cobain and why is he trending?
> 
> — josh⚽ (@\_jjsb) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/_jjsb/status/304265163832426496)

> @[susanrocheyah](https://twitter.com/susanrocheyah) nope I actually don’t know who kurt cobain is… Is that bad…..:
> 
> — anisaa (@anisaa\_97) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/anisaa_97/status/304263565026664450)

> Who is Kurt Cobain ?
> 
> — Sammie (@AeSammie) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/AeSammie/status/304263439059144704)

> Who’s Kurt Cobain??
> 
> — Lace (@alacyah) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/alacyah/status/304262932907323393)

> Who’s kurt cobain?
> 
> — anisaa (@anisaa\_97) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/anisaa_97/status/304262442882588672)

> Lol Who’s Kurt Cobain?
> 
> — Chawlie(@iamfedx) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/iamfedx/status/304261785526079488)

> Who is Kurt Cobain
> 
> — Zoe (@zoetuhrim) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/zoetuhrim/status/304258173857042433)

> Who is Kurt Cobain? Like I’ve never heard of this person. And he’s all I see [#Forreal](https://twitter.com/search/%23Forreal) .
> 
> — Amiya ❤ (@aMiYa\_bOulDiN) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/aMiYa_bOulDiN/status/304253703865655297)

> Quickquestion…err….who’s Kurt Cobain? Wrestler?
> 
> — रागेश नायर (@PurpleSuave) [February 20, 2013](https://twitter.com/PurpleSuave/status/304280570018557952)
